            <title>KatClaw 2026.3.11 (Build 350)</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed gateway token not refreshing after restart or backup restore</li>
                    <li>Wizard now detects npm availability (Node v25+ compatibility)</li>
                    <li>Homebrew users get brew upgrade instead of redundant .pkg install</li>
                    <li>SkillHub registry hidden for non-China users</li>
